âš ï¸ Important Safety Rules

Rotate chemicals (avoid resistance).

Use recommended dose only.

Maintain waiting period before harvest.

Wear gloves, mask, full sleeves.

Avoid spraying during strong wind.

ğŸŒ± Organic / Safer Alternatives

